[SN]TITLE[SN]
CES 2016: Triby adds Amazon Alexa assistant to fridges

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A colourful speaker that brings Amazon's voice-controlled assistant Alexa to your fridge is one of the products being put on display at the CES tech show in Las Vegas.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
2 January 2016 Last updated at 01:17 GMT
The Triby can receive picture messages, make phone calls and answer questions you ask it.
It is the first third-party device to feature Alexa.
BBC's technology desk editor Leo Kelion asked the company's chief Serge Renouard why anyone would need such a gadget in their lives.
